<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="anger-n">anger <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'æŋɡə(r)/    美 /'æŋɡər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>生气；愤怒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>speak <strong>in anger</strong>
气冲冲地说话</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His face turned red with anger.
他气得满脸通红。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>使生气；激怒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is easily angered.
他很容易被激怒。</p></div></div>